chart_description: The system.cpu_some_pressure chart measures the percentage of CPU pressure observed on the system due to some undisclosed processes.

dimension_descriptions.some 10: The percentage of CPU pressure observed on the system over the last 10 seconds
dimension_descriptions.some 300: The percentage of CPU pressure observed on the system over the last 5 minutes
dimension_descriptions.some 60: The percentage of CPU pressure observed on the system over the last minute
